WEBVTT

00:03:29.055 --> 00:03:30.762
But let's be honest.

00:03:30.786 --> 00:03:35.272
Is our 3.5 trillion dollar
health care system

00:03:35.296 --> 00:03:37.650
fundamentally designed to create health?

00:03:38.317 --> 00:03:39.825
Absolutely not.

00:03:40.468 --> 00:03:42.436
Take access to healthy food.

00:03:42.952 --> 00:03:47.116
Not long ago, a teenage boy shows up
at a hospital in Baltimore,

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:48.659
losing weight.

00:03:48.683 --> 00:03:52.615
Just as his doctors are huddled up
figuring out which metabolic panels

00:03:52.639 --> 00:03:54.721
and blood tests to run,

00:03:54.745 --> 00:03:57.084
one of my colleagues asks out loud,

00:03:57.108 --> 00:03:59.191
"Do you think he might be hungry?"